1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
"Karomi ke baare mein sunna?

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Ek startup jiska sapna tha...

3
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:07,200
saare ghar par karahi banaya jaane ki shakti!

4
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:08,400
Makhan, namkeen, paapdi,

5
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:10,800
sabse badi problem thi delivery ki.

6
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:16,000
Logon ko lagta tha ek ghante ki baaziyon tak pakki karne ki aavashyakta.

7
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:18,399
Lekin Karomi ne ek innovation ki.

8
00:00:18,399 --> 00:00:20,399
Usne delivery ki shuruwat ki...

9
00:00:20,399 --> 00:00:22,000
roboton ke madhyam se.

10
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:26,000
Ab toh ghar ghar paani aur garam chaai milte hain...

11
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,199
phir kyun na Karomi ki ghar ghar karahi?

12
00:00:29,199 --> 00:00:34,399
Karomi ke robots aaj tak 1000 se adhik gharon mein khana pakaye hain.

13
00:00:34,399 --> 00:00:39,600
Dusri side, beemariyon ki wajah se bahut log aaj khana pakana seekhte hain.

14
00:00:39,600 --> 00:00:43,200
Karomi ne unke liye bhi ek sahi solution di.

15
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:48,800
Ab unka dil bhi khush ho raha hai aur khana bhi pak raha hai

16
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:57,600
Isliye Karomi ko ek aisi startup kehna jaa sakta hai jo aapke dil ki khwabon ko sach karne ki koshish karti hai.

17
00:00:57,600 --> 00:01:02,400
Karomi ka naya vision... sabhi ke paas khana pakna asaan banane ki!"

